<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | Folder2Txt</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/font-awesome-all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Vazirmatn', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .header h1 i {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .header p {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #334155;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .input-wrapper i {
            position: absolute;
            right: 15px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 50px 15px 20px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
            direction: ltr;
            text-align: left;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: white;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
        }

        input[type="text"]::placeholder {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -5px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -5px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-submit i {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0 20px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #334155;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .feature-item i {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .error-message {
            background: #fee2e2;
            border-right: 5px solid #dc2626;
            color: #991b1b;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            animation: shake 0.5s ease;
        }

        .error-message i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-5px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(5px); }
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer-note i {
            color: #ef4444;
            margin: 0 3px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .card {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>
                <i class="fas fa-folder-open"></i>
                Folder2Txt
            </h1>
            <p>پوشه‌ی خود را به یک فایل متنی یکپارچه تبدیل کنید.</p>
        </div>

        <form action="/process" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="folderPath">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> مسیر پوشه:
                </label>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <i class="fas fa-folder"></i>
                    <input type="text" 
                           id="folderPath" 
                           name="folderPath" 
                           placeholder="/home/user/project  یا  C:\myproject" 
                           required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">
                <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> پردازش و دریافت خروجی
                <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
            </button>
        </form>

        <% if (locals.error) { %>
            <div class="error-message">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                <span><%= error %></span>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="features">
            <span class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-code"></i> تشخیص خودکار باینری</span>
            <span class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-tree"></i> نمایش درخت پوشه</span>
            <span class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> خروجی یکپارچه</span>
            <span class="feature-item"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> امن و خصوصی</span>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-note">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 
            پوشه‌های <strong>node_modules</strong>، <strong>.git</strong> و فایل‌های باینری نادیده گرفته می‌شوند.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>